        "name": "Steppers completo",
        "content": "\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\n  <div class=\"row\">\n    <div class=\"col-12\">\n      <div class=\"steppers\">\n        <div class=\"steppers-header mb-3\">\n          <ul>\n            <li class=\"confirmed\">Primo contenuto <svg class=\"icon steppers-success\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"https://italia.github.io/bootstrap-italia/dist/svg/sprites.svg#it-check\"></use></svg><span class=\"visually-hidden\">Confermato</span></li>\n            <li class=\"active\">Secondo contenuto <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Attivo</span></li>\n            <li>Terzo contenuto</li>\n          </ul>\n          <span class=\"steppers-index\" aria-hidden=\"true\">2/6</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"steppers-content mb-3\" aria-live=\"polite\">\n          <!-- Esempio START -->\n          <p>Contenuto di esempio dello step corrente</p>\n          <!-- Esempio END -->\n        </div>\n        <nav class=\"steppers-nav mb-3\">\n          <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-icon btn-outline-primary btn-sm steppers-btn-prev\"><svg class=\"icon icon-sm icon-primary\"><use href=\"https://italia.github.io/bootstrap-italia/dist/svg/sprites.svg#it-chevron-left\"></use></svg>Indietro</button>\n          <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-icon btn-primary btn-sm steppers-btn-next\">Avanti <svg class=\"icon icon-sm icon-inverse\"><use href=\"https://italia.github.io/bootstrap-italia/dist/svg/sprites.svg#it-chevron-right\"></use></svg></button>\n        </nav>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n"
